title: Statistics Canada, Top 5 Canadian Imports by Country, World, 1995-2002
name: Statistics Canada, Top 5 Canadian Imports by Country, World, 1995-2002
description:
This dataset represents the top five countries to import into Canada for the years 1995 - 2002. This data is from Statistics Canada. 

The total imports for each year are as follows in million of Canadian dollars: 1995 - $ 225,553, 1996 - $232,566, 1997 - $272,946, 1998 - $298,386, 1999 - $320,409, 2000 - $356,862, 2001 - $343,076, 2002 - $348,445.
